{"tid":2171153,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[高質港台節目] 中國式‧是咁的-中國篇","createTime":"2020-08-23T18:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:39:09.000Z","uid":55360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9e5dce719b9e1437522c802bcef7fd3e9f9f02","tid":2171153,"uid":55360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PnFgKKoG2I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPnFgKKoG2I0&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=3afdd335\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PnFgKKoG2I0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國式‧是咁的:中國篇</strong><br />\n中國一路向外經濟擴張，但內部經濟充滿隱憂。<br />\n中央政府提出鄉村振興，改善農村環境‵、拉動內需，但又出現發展商的一窩蜂發展，全國各地出現不少盲目建設的失敗小鎮，而在改造過程中的拆遷賠償問題，又暴露出中國式鄉鎮發展老問題。<br />\n<br />\n而家先發現原來係一年前既節目<br />\n真係好高質，有做實地考察同做足功課"},{"pid":"9a1c8392f3f1c8fcebe73490af2b878509660f40","tid":2171153,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔係你估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />任何節目,只要是RTHK有參與的,你都會知道是高質的丶專業的、持平的"},{"pid":"1f5cebed1852f377010ebcea7268c0bf8d2db34a","tid":2171153,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T19:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48b69f4cafe380decc9cecbe1b734b783aa16dd7","tid":2171153,"uid":55360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}